DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T150000
SUMMARY:KHTA Adopters and Mainteners Work Day - April 4
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\n**KHTA V
 olunteers & Adopters Workdays – April 4**\n\nWe have made considerable p
 rogress since the beginning of the year clearing trail\, building drains\,
  and chainsawing blowdowns from mile 34 to mile 35.5 (Hwy 56). We will con
 tinue maintenance of the trail on the North side of Highway 56\nDetails wi
 ll be posted here\, on Meetup\, and Facebook. We will continue to meet on 
 the North side of Hwy 56 at the trail crossing.\nWe will park at the trail
  crossing of North Level Road Ratt Road. From the Elk Creek Lake entrance 
 head west up the hill for about 1.3 miles. For Google directions click on 
 [Highway 56 Trail Crossing](https://maps.app.goo.gl/Pm8WyrtSzUbcerDk9)\nPl
 ease bring a lunch and water. We will have large hand tools\, you may brin
 g any small tools you have such as clippers or a pruning saw. And a backpa
 ck is handy to carry everything in. Instructions will be provided for thos
 e who need them. We will finish at about 3:00.\nSign up on [Meetup](https:
 //www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of-indiana-meetup/even
 ts/312393553/?eventOrigin=group_upcoming_events)\nJoin us on our website a
 t [http://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/](http://www.knobstonehikingtrail.o
 rg/) and on Facebook at [KHTA Facebook Group.](https://www.facebook.com/gr
 oups/2255586117953484/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of
 -indiana-meetup/events/313931312/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260324T202554Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260324T202554Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of-indiana-meetup/
UID:event_312918119@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260403T025746Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T151500
SUMMARY:2nd Weekend Work Day Trail Building
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\nWould yo
 u to spend a day in some beautiful woods with a delightful group of people
  building a connecting section of Indiana’s premier long distance hiking
  trail? Come join us as we continue work on the Tecumseh Trail extension p
 ortion of the KHT in MMSF. We will be building the new trail including cli
 pping green briar.\nPlease bring a lunch and water. We will have large han
 d tools\, but please bring any small tools you have such as clippers or a 
 pruning saw. And a backpack is handy to carry everything in. Instructions 
 will be provided for those who need them. We finish about 3:30.\nMeet at t
 he Hatfield Ridge Road gate. The gate is locked but we have a key. Go to t
 he big sign on Rosenbaum/Catholic Cemetry Rd.\nJoin us on our website at h
 ttp://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/\, on Facebook at [www.facebook.com/gro
 ups/2255586117953484](http://www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484)\, a
 nd Substack [https://khta.substack.com/](https://khta.substack.com/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of
 -indiana-meetup/events/312918119/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260116T195304Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T195304Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
